title: CAMIE v1.0
description:
The player is an insect, a beautiful little ladybug called "Camie" that spends most of her time walking on a majestic tree in the middle of a vast field. 

Camie is on a very important mission: to eliminate aphids that live in that tree. Aphids spend their days eating the tree's leaves, and that is very harmful to the tree.

To achieve her goal, our ladybug has some trump cards. She moves quickly and conducts flights of a few seconds each. 

She is therefore very agile in capturing aphids. Also, she should be wary of certain enemies, such as the giant spider and the raven that sometimes make an appearance, attempting to capture it.

More Info:
